title: Daily Wire Backstage: The Mask Is Off
description:
Can Biden’s daily regimen of Gatorade, PB&J’s, and Flintstone Vitamins really keep him in the tip top cognitive shape we’ve come to expect? Is there a certain number of rockets fired by Hamas at Israeli civilians that would convince the Left they’re on the “wrong side of history?” Because clearly, 3500 isn’t it. And when the UFOs playing peek-a-boo with our military do finally land, will John Cena apologize to our alien overlords for Hollywood’s shame that is The Last Jedi, Battlefield Earth, and Howard The Duck? Let’s hope he does the right thing. 
Join this roundtable discussion featuring Ben Shapiro, Andrew Klavan, Matt Walsh, Michael Knowles, and Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing to find out!
